OL,3,CLive facial recognition to be expanded
OL,4,Cfor neighbourhood policing
OL,6,FLive facial recognition will be
OL,7,Fexpanded across the country as part of
OL,8,Fa Government remodel of neighbourhood
OL,9,Fpolicing.
OL,11,FThe technology will be introduced to
OL,12,Fcatch "high-harm" offenders, with new
OL,13,Frules drawn up to support its use and
OL,14,Fensure "safeguards and oversight", the
OL,15,FHome Office said.
OL,17,FTen vans equipped with cameras will be
OL,18,Frolled out across seven police forces,
OL,19,Fincluding Greater Manchester Police,
OL,20,Fover the coming weeks.
