OL,3,CLive facial recognition to be expanded
OL,4,Cfor neighbourhood policing
OL,6,FOther forces include West Yorkshire,
OL,7,FBedfordshire, Surrey, Sussex, Thames
OL,8,FValley and Hampshire.
OL,10,FExisting rules require checks only to
OL,11,Fbe done against police watchlists of
OL,12,Fwanted criminals, suspects and those
OL,13,Fsubject to bail or court order
OL,14,Fconditions like sex offenders.
OL,16,FHowever, a Government consultation
OL,17,Fwill launch in the autumn to help
OL,18,F"shape a new legal framework" on its
OL,19,Fuse.
