OL,3,CLive facial recognition to be expanded
OL,4,Cfor neighbourhood policing
OL,6,FThe vans will be manned by trained
OL,7,Fofficers and individual forces will
OL,8,Fdecide how and when they are deployed.
OL,10,FPrivacy campaigners have previously
OL,11,Fvoiced concerns about a potential lack
OL,12,Fof regulation and transparency over
OL,13,Fthe expansion of the technology.
OL,15,FYvette Cooper, Home Secretary, said
OL,16,Fthey would be focused on identifying
OL,17,Fsex offenders or "people wanted for
OL,18,Fthe most serious crimes who the police
OL,19,Fhave not been able to find."
